HOW TO: install davit-py for development (SD-lab install)?

1.  	in a terminal, move to the parent folder where you want to install davitpy
2.  	type 'git clone https://github.com/vtsuperdarn/davitpy.git'
3.  	add the following lines to your ~/.bashrc

		export DAVITPY="path_to_the_davitpy_directory"
		export PATH=${DAVITPY}"/bin":${PATH}

4.	open a new terminal, type 'davitpy', and enjoy